      "author_association" : "CONTRIBUTOR",
      "body" : "Hm, just curious: is there another practical way to pause a functional test besides pdb? Anyway, since it doesn't hurt, I added it back now :)",
      "commit_id" : "afdcfb237e0d86f65eaceff9c3abc181c6f5576e",
